  "trailer": {
    "title": "WHERE IS MY MONEY | Game Design - 3D Animation",
    "sections": [
        {
            "type": "text",
            "paddingTop": 0,
            "html": "<div><span class=\"texteditor-inline-color\" style=\"color:#111111;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\" class=\"texteditor-inline-fontsize\"><span style=\"font-family:ttyp; font-weight:700;\">YEAR : </span><span style=\"font-family:ftnk; font-weight:400;\">2023</span></span></span></div><div><span class=\"texteditor-inline-color\" style=\"color:#111111;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\" class=\"texteditor-inline-fontsize\"><span style=\"font-family:ttyp; font-weight:700;\">SOFTWARE :</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:15px;\" class=\"texteditor-inline-fontsize\"><span style=\"font-family:ftnk; font-weight:400;\">BLENDER, ADOBE ILLUSTRATOR, PHOTOSHOP, PREMIERE PRO, AFTER EFFECTS, UNITY</span></span></span></div><div><span class=\"texteditor-inline-color\" style=\"color:#111111;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\" class=\"texteditor-inline-fontsize\"><span style=\"font-family:ftnk; font-weight:400;\">“Where Is My Money” is a narrative-driven 3D interactive game that explores the real-life issue of unexpected fund loss in bank accounts—one of the most concerning financial problems today. Through immersive 3D graphics and a first-person perspective, the game guides players through a fictional scenario inspired by true events. It aims to raise awareness, simulate real reactions, and offer appropriate solution suggestions, helping users better understand the complexity of such situations in a visually engaging way.</span></span></span></div>"
        },
        {
            "type": "video",
            "paddingTop": 0,
            "iframeSrc": "https://www-ccv.adobe.io/v1/player/ccv/TFTvIZLYemP/embed?bgcolor=%23191919&lazyLoading=true&api_key=BehancePro2View",
            "aspectPadding": 56.25,
            "maxWidth": 1920
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "paddingTop": 0,
            "html": "<div><span class=\"texteditor-inline-fontsize\" style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-family:ftnk;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color:#111111;\" class=\"texteditor-inline-color\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/the.penguins_space/\">@the.penguins_space</a> - Anh nguyen • 3D Artist, 3D Motion Designer, 3D Coder<br><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/prettyaw.f/\">@prettyaw.f</a> - Anh quach • 2D Artist, UIUX, 2D Coder<br><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/bbaebear.__/\">@bbaebear.__</a> - Hiep NInh • 3D Artist, 3D Motion Designer, Sound Designer<br><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/binart.xinkout/\">@binart.xinkout</a> - Phat Le • 2D Designer, Video Editor, Sound Designer</span></span></span></div>"
        }
    ]
},
